node.text: On the occasion of Chinese New Year, Pulitzer Prize-winning author @iandenisjohnson invites readers through the magnificent and storied palace built by China’s Yongle Emperor to serve as the seat of the Ming dynasty in #ForbiddenCity, the latest addition to Assouline’s Ultimate Collection. #ChineseNewYear

node.title: Forbidden City: The Palace at the Heart of Chinese Culture
